description:
Watching all of this unfold and seeing how easily people were manipulated into giving up their liberties for some sort of fake protection makes me think, what would happen if there was a truly deadly virus like that of the black plague or smallpox that hit the nation how quickly would people submit to governmental tyranny?  This sets a precedent to show how quickly those in control  Will drink from the goblet of power until completely drunk and then continue to drink more. If there is one thing that I pray for and hope for in the future it is that we all take a lesson from what we have learned and make a change so that it doesn't happen again in the future.
